title: Leverock's Great Seafood - St. Petersburg, FL
snippet: Since 1948, Leverock's has been providing quality, value, and service. Our dining room is casual, so come as you are. We are located just off of St. Pete Beach in the South Pasadena area of St. Petersburg, Florida. See you soon!

title: Leverock's Great Seafood - St. Petersburg, FL - Yelp
snippet: Specialties: We are a casual seafood restaurant with full service and full bar. Established in 1948. Johnny Leverock opened an oyster bar in 1948, after winning local oyster beds in a poker game. It grew into a full service family restaurant over the years.
